# Website QA before merge

Run through these manually or ask the agent to verify after UI changes:

## Mobile menu

- [ ] Hamburger opens/closes nav drawer on ≤ 768px
- [ ] Focus bar follows touch/drag on menu items
- [ ] Shop + Gaming mode buttons visible and tappable
- [ ] Language switcher cycles en → roman → ur without layout break

## Shop / cart

- [ ] Product grid loads from `/api/products`
- [ ] Add to cart, quantity change, remove item work
- [ ] Checkout form submits order; success/error messages show
- [ ] Open/closed badge reflects shop status API

## Repair form

- [ ] Device + issue selection works on mobile
- [ ] Screen quality picker (if shown) selects and persists
- [ ] Booking submits; WhatsApp link optional path works
- [ ] Form validation messages use `t()` in all langs

## Staff (if touched)

- [ ] Login/logout; staff toolbar only when authenticated
- [ ] Add product modal saves; chat inbox polls only when visible tab

## Build

- [ ] `npm run build` passes with no errors
- [ ] No console errors on home, shop, gaming, repair, contact routes
